cross: Paphiopedilum Ninja x Paphiopedilum Enchantingly Wood

measurements.description: One flower on one inflorescence; sepals white, veined green; petals cream overlaid green, faint fine darker green veins, heavily spotted mahogany, margins hirsute; pouch green, upper portion overlaid mahogany, veined mahogany; staminode green; substance firm; texture matte.
